productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 kilogram!!!
I saw one of these in Libya and I bought one.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
